HEADWORD: Scutiger
<hw>Scu"ti*ger</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[NL., fr. L.
<ets>scutum</ets> shield + <ets>gerere</ets> to bear.]</ety>
<fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>Any species of chilopod myriapods of the genus
<gen>Scutigera</gen>. They sometimes enter buildings and prey upon
insects.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

